---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "December 11, 2024";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for mattglbrt.com">
  <article class="glass p-6 sm:p-8 prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-white/60">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <p>This Privacy Policy describes how mattglbrt.com ("the Site," "we," "us") collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit or interact with the Site.</p>

    <p>By using this Site, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>

    <p>For questions, contact:<br />
    Email: <a href="mailto:matt@goeveryway.com">matt@goeveryway.com</a></p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information in the following ways:</p>

    <h3>A. Information You Voluntarily Provide</h3>
    <p>When you:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Subscribe to the newsletter</li>
      <li>Submit a contact form</li>
      <li>Comment (if comments are enabled)</li>
      <li>Download resources</li>
    </ul>

    <p>You may provide:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Name</li>
      <li>Email address</li>
      <li>Any message you type or content you submit</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>B. Automatically Collected Information</h3>
    <p>When you visit the Site, certain data is collected automatically through:</p>

    <h4>1. Google Analytics</h4>
    <p>We use Google Analytics to understand website traffic and usage patterns. This may include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your IP address (may be anonymized depending on region)</li>
      <li>Device and browser information</li>
      <li>Pages viewed and time spent</li>
      <li>Referral sources</li>
      <li>General geographic location (non-precise)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Google may place cookies or other tracking technologies to perform this analysis.</p>
    <p>You can learn more or opt out here: <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites</a></p>

    <h4>2. Cloudflare</h4>
    <p>Cloudflare provides security, caching, and performance optimization. Cloudflare may collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>IP address</li>
      <li>System/browser information</li>
      <li>Security threat indicators</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This helps protect the Site from malicious traffic.</p>
    <p>Learn more: <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/</a></p>

    <h4>3. Netlify</h4>
    <p>We use Netlify to host the website. Netlify may collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Server logs</li>
      <li>IP addresses</li>
      <li>Error logs</li>
      <li>Performance metrics</li>
    </ul>
    <p>This data is used for security, debugging, and hosting reliability.</p>
    <p>Netlify privacy policy: <a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.netlify.com/privacy/</a></p>

    <h2>2. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
    <p>The Site uses cookies for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Analytics (Google Analytics)</li>
      <li>Performance and security (Cloudflare)</li>
      <li>Remembering preferences (if applicable)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You may disable cookies in your browser settings, though some features may not function correctly.</p>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We may use collected information to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Operate and maintain the website</li>
      <li>Understand how users interact with the Site</li>
      <li>Improve content, performance, and user experience</li>
      <li>Send newsletters or updates if you subscribed</li>
      <li>Respond to messages or inquiries</li>
      <li>Protect the Site from spam, abuse, or security threats</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>We do not sell personal information to third parties.</strong></p>

    <h2>4. Email Newsletter</h2>
    <p>If you subscribe to the newsletter, your name and email address will be stored by a third-party email provider (e.g., Mailchimp, ConvertKit, Beehiiv, etc.).</p>
    <p>Your information is used only to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Send newsletters</li>
      <li>Deliver updates, announcements, or content</li>
      <li>Manage subscriber lists</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You may unsubscribe at any time via the link in any email.</p>

    <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>The Site may include links or integrations with external services including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Google</li>
      <li>Cloudflare</li>
      <li>Netlify</li>
      <li>Email newsletter platforms</li>
      <li>Embedded YouTube videos or social content</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These third parties may collect data according to their own privacy policies. We do not control their practices.</p>

    <h2>6. Embedded Content</h2>
    <p>Posts may include embedded content (videos, images, articles). Embedded content behaves as if you visited the third-party website directly. Those sites may collect data, use cookies, or track your interaction.</p>

    <h2>7. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain data only as long as necessary for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Operating the Site</li>
      <li>Analytics</li>
      <li>Newsletters</li>
      <li>Legal compliance</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You may request deletion of your personal data at any time (contact information below).</p>

    <h2>8. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your region, you may have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Access your data</li>
      <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
      <li>Request deletion</li>
      <li>Request a copy of your data</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent</li>
      <li>Opt out of analytics cookies</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To make a request, email: <a href="mailto:matt@goeveryway.com">matt@goeveryway.com</a></p>

    <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>This Site is not intended for individuals under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>

    <h2>10. Security</h2>
    <p>We use reasonable technical and organizational measures—including Cloudflare protection and secure hosting—to safeguard your data. However, no system is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute protection.</p>

    <h2>11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Updates will be posted on this page with a new "Last updated" date.</p>
    <p>Continued use of the Site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised policy.</p>

    <h2>12. Contact Information</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or want to request access or deletion of your data, contact:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: <a href="mailto:matt@goeveryway.com">matt@goeveryway.com</a></li>
      <li>Site: <a href="https://mattglbrt.com">https://mattglbrt.com</a></li>
    </ul>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .prose {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .prose h1, .prose h2, .prose h3, .prose h4 {
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .prose h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .prose h3 {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .prose h4 {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .prose a {
    color: #3b82f6;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .prose a:hover {
    color: #2563eb;
  }

  .prose ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
</style>
